In [111]:
l = df.bill_length_mm
df.bill_length_mm = l.fillna(l.mean()) # Fills the NaN with average
d = df.bill_depth_mm
df.bill_depth_mm = d.fillna(d.mean())
f = df.flipper_length_mm
df.flipper_length_mm = f.fillna(f.mean())
b = df.body_mass_g
df.body_mass_g = b.fillna(b.mean())

In [121]:
def print_silhouette_score(features):
   print("Silhouette Coefficient with feature", *features, ": \n" + str(metrics.silhouette_score(df[features], km.labels_, metric='euclidean')))
